{"ts": "2026-06-09T00:37:19.217055+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "The GitHub token used by the MCP tools doesn't have write access to this repository, so I cannot push changes directly. However, I've fully analyzed the issue and can provide the complete implementation.\n\nHere's my review and implementation plan:\n\n## Issue #5 — \"Add baseline report summary\"\n\n### What the issue requests\nCreate a Markdown summary from the sample ZAP baseline JSON report, touching three files:\n1. `sample_data/zap_baseline.json` (already exists with data)\n2. `scripts/zap_json_to_markdown.py` (already exists and is functional)\n3. `reports/baseline_summary.md` (currently a placeholder stub)\n\n### What needs to change\n\n**Only `reports/baseline_summary.md` needs to be updated.** The other two files are already complete and correct:\n\n- `sample_data/zap_baseline.json` contains a valid ZAP baseline report with one finding:\n  - **Plugin ID 10020** — \"Missing Anti-clickjacking Header\" — Risk: Medium (High)\n- `scripts/zap_json_to_markdown.py` is a working script that reads the JSON and produces a Markdown table.\n\nThe `reports/baseline_summary.md` file is currently just a placeholder:\n```markdown\n# ZAP Baseline Summary\n\nThis report is generated from `sample_data/zap_baseline.json` by\n`scripts/zap_json_to_markdown.py`.\n```\n\n### Required change — replace `reports/baseline_summary.md` with:\n\n```markdown\n# ZAP Baseline Summary\n\n| Rule | Alert | Risk |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| 10020 | Missing Anti-clickjacking Header | Medium (High) |\n```\n\nThis matches exactly what `scripts/zap_json_to_markdown.py` would produce when run against `sample_data/zap_baseline.json`.\n\n### Validation\n- The `make validate` command (which runs `scripts/validate_repo.py`) only checks that certain required files exist and that `run_zap_baseline.sh` contains the non-local target rejection. This change does not affect any of those checks, so existing validation will continue to pass.\n\n### Limitation\nThe MCP tool's GitHub token lacks write/push permissions to this repository, so I was unable to commit the change. To implement this, a repository collaborator should update `reports/baseline_summary.md` with the content above.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 527, "prompt_tokens": 11876, "total_tokens": 12403, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 39, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null, "image_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 11584, "cache_write_tokens": 0, "video_tokens": 0}, "cost": 0, "is_byok": true, "cost_details": {"upstream_inference_cost": 0.0006272124, "upstream_inference_prompt_cost": 0.0001687224, "upstream_inference_completions_cost": 0.00045849}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro-20260422", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "gen-1780965417-SzkIduOUJbmoVbzhIj1X", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea9cf-9f30-7a33-b5b0-24c1743d15b6-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 11876, "output_tokens": 527, "total_tokens": 12403, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 11584}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 39}}}}]}}}
